posts.body: I tried pressing seed a few minutes after posting. I can't seem to seed my own image. Is there an option to seed what you post by default?

>tfw cant make sense of it

edit: I have zeronet set to download and seed all of 8chan but I can't seed my own? Does the image just go out into the nether?
Well, it looks like most the the images in this thread are fugged, must be something going on with the board then?

http://127.0.0.1:43110/1DdPHedr5Tz55EtQWxqvsbEXPdc4uCVi9D/?:users/14r48CcSSyoNo1PNhy6uWriqpopMUfqfUX:tech:25e41ec7-13d5-4a07-881a-b3b05b3ec8a1

This looks like a possible fix, but seems like you need to be able to compilers and a terminal, and I am but a lowly windows pleb. Maybe the board owner(s?) could deploy this site wide?
